-- Turkey's Alternatifbank secures syndication loan in euro and dollar tranches
-- By Ebru Tuncay
-- Thu Jun 12, 2014 02:51AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, June 12 (Reuters) - Turkey's Alternatifbank <ALNTF.IS> has secured a syndication loan in two tranches of 114 million euros ($155 million) and $189.5 million, it said in a filing with the Istanbul stock exchange on Thursday.

